title: syntax & evaluation strategy
pid: 79ce3359-c068-4e5f-b95b-b1cf87e6cebe
body: |2-
  Each line is evaluated,
  and the result of its last expression is displayed.
  Semicolons divide expressions on the same line.
  [[id:e7ff348a-2c91-4be3-9ce2-c663091995f7][Pipes bind more tightly than semicolons.]]
misc:
- Had_ID_Before_Import
